Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:06.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:52.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:11.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:06.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:52.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:11.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:43.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:49.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:58.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:06.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:15.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:23.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:30.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:39.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:47.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:55.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:43.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:49.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤獨中尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:58.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用靈魂連結我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:06.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用愛戀溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:15.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那顫抖的祈願之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:23.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:30.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不斷交替的輪迴之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:39.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不終結的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:47.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷輪迴的 那些傳頌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:55.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守護著安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼燒著…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…喉嚨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被灼燒著…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 好好地安睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不可以亂動的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口還會痛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這裡是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你倒在了森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你的時候 你受了很重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶說過你已經度過了危險期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白 我是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…到底…是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼無法摘下來 因為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎醒過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和恩人打一下招呼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 艾露露不用操心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個面具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘不下來的話自然有其中的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你只需專心養病就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熬了些粥過來 摩洛洛粥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩洛洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃一點有營養的東西的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了身為見習藥師分內的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧 不然要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說 還很燙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是兒子的舊衣服 但穿上去正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 正合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就打算去四處走一走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不能總是由你們來照顧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在還是靜養一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 跟著他一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在路上突然倒下了也很讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好照顧他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 來好好打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 她是我妹妹阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像誤會了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那孩子一定是因為看到你穿著父親的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 怎麼沒看到他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親已經去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親也在生下阿露露後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能借用這麼珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經是我們小時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很感謝你攙扶著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣你會很累的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 邊境的女孩子可是很強壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境的女孩的確很強壯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你突然去摸人家女孩子的尾巴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真正的尾巴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵奧羅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抬到村長那裡的奇怪傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 很奇怪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了流民外很少有客人來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有流民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡比其他地方要和平 時不時會有流民過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是個什麼都沒有的小村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都過得非常快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很多正在修理中的房屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間發生了一次巨大的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候因為阿露露沒有回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露鬧得雞犬不寧的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 平安無事不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 又把工作曬一邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽出來之前我都有在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裂了 要裂了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 索波克姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是被抬到艾露露家的奇怪男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 連索波克姐姐都這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對晚熟的艾露露來說 這不是很積極嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個人受了傷 所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你是不是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索波克姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我勉強讓你出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想要到外面來轉轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會就要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在這裡休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好給我聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起將再次增加年貢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為了國家盡上一份力 很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣 太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要遵從我們的吩咐來做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我又為了見你而飛奔過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 是匹不錯的騎龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為脾氣暴躁所以只有我才能駕馭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 竟敢違逆主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個傢伙在笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說是鄉下人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以說自己故鄉的壞話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想聽 不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明不會說這樣的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是以前 現在是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徵收完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 先下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會滿足於這樣的窮鄉僻壤的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟我一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好了嗎 帶你一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那樣約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我不是說過要讓你過上奢侈的生活的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要奢侈的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上沒有人不想過奢侈生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒那麼希望過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到她不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是知道的話 就不會感到苦惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把面具給我摘下來 然後向努旺基大人我請安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個面具摘不下來 而且也沒理由向你請安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像沒明白本大人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說鄉下人讓人為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大人是努旺基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好隱瞞的 是這個國家的皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的弟弟 統治這裡的藩主 薩桑迪的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為嚇壞了而說不出話來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從什麼時候開始讓這種可疑的傢伙呆在村裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把他趕出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者就讓本大人現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人並不是什麼可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在較什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和他在一起生活 所以我知道他是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說奇怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經有我這個男人在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只不過是普通的青梅竹馬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是…只不過是算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 這傢伙突然出現在這裡算什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是不能不管 於是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我之間怎麼容得下礙事的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 事辦完了嗎 王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相干的傢伙 給我滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有充足的相干關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的恩人 同時也是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有說什麼讓你不高興的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都沒怎麼說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話 我是感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒感到麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努旺基 以前明明不是那樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 世上沒有人自出生開始就利慾熏心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡 可惡 可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藐視我 反駁我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大 那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是「主」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是有人捉弄了靈碑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼過分的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人 一直和我在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這我們都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒有懷疑小哥 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在談很重要的事 來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被懷疑也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說嘛 這些傢伙也只是有點害怕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問「主」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是森林之神的使者 森林的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我們破壞森林 一直在守護著它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快去平息它的怒氣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就不能進入森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 乾脆打倒它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在胡說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼可能是森林之神的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」大人強壯 敏捷 聰慧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且再加上那刀槍不入的身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果魯莽地去刺激它 只會以我們的慘敗而告終
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈碑果然遭到破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那馬上把它修復 再獻上平息怒氣的貢品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也下得越來越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈沒理由為了這種小事而動怒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是這樣覺得而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 入夜後大家盡量不要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等雨一停就去修復靈碑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經沒有在出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了艾露露的護理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為奶奶的藥的關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶是天下第一的藥師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為何會說那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥冥中有什麼東西在觸動著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己 給大家帶來了不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽牛角尖對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在請專心想著讓身體好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要身體恢復了 記憶也一定會隨之恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽艾露露你這麼說 我安心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露會成為出色的藥師的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝


